Quick start

1. Install dependencies
   pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Validate live controller connectivity
   python clint_test.py

3. Evaluate a trained model
   python evaluate.py --config prod.json --model-path models/dqn_model.pth

4. Train on live environment
   python train.py --config prod.json --model-path models/dqn_model_live.pth
